$aIssued Mar. 1, 1922-June 24, 1939 by Bureau of Agricultural Economics; Jan. 5, 1931-Sept. 14, 1936, Jan.-June 1939 by its Foreign Agricultural Service; July 1, 1939-Mar. 16, 1953 by Office of Foreign Agricultural Relations.

$aFrom 1937 to 1945 statistical supplements entitled "United States foreign trade in agricultural products" were issued. Beginning in 1946 these publications were issued separately in three different serials: Foreign agricultural trade. United States foreign trade in agricultural products. Fiscal year ... with comparisons; Foreign agricultural trade. United States foreign trade in agricultural products. Calendar year ... with comparisons; and: Foreign agricultural trade.
$aHas monthly suppl.: Mar. 1957-1962 Foreign crops and markets. World summaries, crops and livestock; 1963, Foreign crops and markets. Statistical supplement.
$aMerged with: Foreign agriculture, to form: Foreign agriculture (Washington, D.C. : 1963).
